metadata.name: PMONDA - BALANCE
metadata.description:
"PMONDA" 

The first image of this collection of 5 pieces, where we can appreciate the importance of separating our work space from our living space. 

This is an invitation to project ourselves in the professionalism and excellence that we can achieve if we separate the ecosystems in a perfect balance.

The invitation to create a frame and bring this digital artwork to life on the "material plane" is always welcome.
